metadata.description: WAYC | Empowering Women in Web 3.0 | Are You Feeling Lonely Bored Ape Yacht Club (BAYC)? Compare our WAYC NFTs with real world women personalities and Tag us on twitter @womenapeyc! Some Lucky people will get chance to win WAYC NFTs giveaway.Every WAYC holder will get a Mutant Women Apes for free. Only gas fees will be charged. Discover our fabulous Women Apes and grab the one that makes your heart skip a beat before others do! Bored ape are welcome to find there life companion. This project is launched by the 99xClub Team. 99x Club Membership pass can be minted by WAYC holders only. 99x Club membership pass will have numerous benefits.For more details, visit our website https://womenapeyachtclub.com/ or discord : https://discord.com/invite/8RyrCxkDVr
